23:27.272 --> 23:30.442
Oh, thank you very much.

23:30.509 --> 23:32.778
Oh, your skin is so soft.

23:32.844 --> 23:33.845
Are you young?

23:33.912 --> 23:35.781
Um, yeah.

23:35.847 --> 23:37.048
Thanks.

23:38.617 --> 23:41.553
