say something.

23:57.135 --> 23:59.271
Someone should.

23:59.337 --> 24:01.673
I'm probably not going to be
the person who says something.

24:01.740 --> 24:03.375
I probably won't either.

24:04.743 --> 24:06.444
Got everything?

24:04.743 --> 24:06.444
I think so.

24:08.413 --> 24:10.415
Oh, there's your buddy.

24:10.482 --> 24:12.350
